//www.project2025.observer/" target="_blank" data-v-14b8a95c>the outstanding work put forth by the Project 2025 Tracker team</a>, we’re here to break it down for you. We can&#39;t trust our legislators to put in their due diligence, and as <a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/gop-congressman-calls-out-marjorie-taylor-greenes-stock-trades-2025-5" target="_blank" data-v-14b8a95c>they&#39;ve already proven</a>, they are in a unique position to take advantage of the political landscape to benefit their own pockets. If we stop paying attention, they get away with even more. </p></section><section data-v-14b8a95c><h1 data-v-14b8a95c>How?</h1><p class="center-text" data-v-14b8a95c> Fight 🔥 with 🐲. We’re using AI to help us sift through the legalese and research everything <em data-v-14b8a95c>rápidamente</em>, because how the fuck are <strong data-v-14b8a95c><em data-v-14b8a95c>We, The People</em></strong> supposed to be able to read and comprehend this <a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/trumps-big-beautiful-bill-over-235628822.html" target="_blank" data-v-14b8a95c>23,450 line Bill</a> in time to be able to give our representatives feedback before <a href="https://apnews.com/article/trump-big-bill-senate-gop-debt-a0679756c6af762ac0291be6cb647145" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-v-14b8a95c>the vote on the 4th of July</a> otherwise?! I sure can&#39;t, so lets take advantage of Big Tech to help us fight back while we still can. </p><p class="center-text inline" data-v-14b8a95c> Because AI cannot be trusted, we humans are going through every single section as quickly as possible and verifying them to ensure everything is both accurate and up-to-date. </p><p class="inline" data-v-14b8a95c> Sections which are already verified by human beings will have a <i class="verified" data-v-14b8a95c>✔</i> before them. </p><p class="inline" data-v-14b8a95c> Those which are unverified will have a <i data-v-14b8a95c>?</i>. </p><p data-v-14b8a95c> If you would like to volunteer to join us (please, please help 😀), just send us a message at one of our contacts (listed below) with what you&#39;d be available to help with, and we&#39;ll go from there. </p></section><section data-v-14b8a95c><h1 data-v-14b8a95c>Coming Soon</h1><ul data-v-14b8a95c><li data-v-14b8a95c>Viewing sections from more than one title/subtitle/part/subpart simultaneously.</li><li data-v-14b8a95c>Verification of all information by human reviewers.</li><li data-v-14b8a95c>Notes about which sections are subject to the Byrd Rule.</li></ul></section><section class="contact" data-v-14b8a95c><h1 data-v-14b8a95c>Contact Us</h1><div data-v-14b8a95c><a href="https://github.com/foxtrot-delta-tango" target="_blank" data-v-14b8a95c>GitHub</a><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/big-bullshit-bill.bsky.social" target="_blank" data-v-14b8a95c>BlueSky</a><a href="mailto:big.bullshid.bill@gmail.com" data-v-14b8a95c>Email</a></div></section>',4)]))}const uf=ze(lf,[["render",df],["__scopeId","data-v-14b8a95c"]]),hf={},pf={class:"whats-next"};function ff(e,n){const t=wa("router-link");return M(),G("div",pf,[v("section",null,[n[7]||(n[7]=v("h1",null,"How can I fight back?",-1)),n[8]||(n[8]=v("p",null,[Y(" Are you "),v("a",{href:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGIY5Vyj4YM",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer"},"mad as hell"),Y("? Are you not going to take this anymore? ")],-1)),n[9]||(n[9]=v("p",null," Do you want to do something about it?! ",-1)),n[10]||(n[10]=v("p",null," Well, you’re not alone! Many Americans are feeling the 🔥 right now. ",-1)),n[11]||(n[11]=v("p",null," Here are a list of suggestions on how to channel your energy into action: ",-1)),v("ul",null,[n[3]||(n[3]=v("li",null,[Y("Contact your representatives to make your voice heard with the help of a utility like "),v("a",{href:"https://5calls.org/",target:"_blank"},"5Calls.org"),Y(", a fantastic website that helps provide you with prompts and information to easily make five calls to your representatives.")],-1)),v("li",nul